data.description: This gorgeous, extremely well-maintained four bedroom home is located in the highly sought after Encino Estates subdivision. Encino Estates embodies the perfect combination of country living and a warm, welcoming suburban atmosphere.     On almost nearly an acre of land, this home is nestled away with no back neighbors and an an adorable back porch ideal for deer watching.     The interior features an open-concept floor plan with tons of natural light and high ceilings throughout. The kitchen showcases a large center island, ample cabinet space and all stainless steel appliances. The primary suite features an elegant tray ceiling outlined with crown molding, an oversized bathroom with a soaking tub, separate shower and private toilet room and a walk-in closet. The three guest bedrooms are spacious with sizable closets.     Also, seller is offering a full appliance package!!     You need to see this one for yourself... schedule your showing today!
